overview:
Larry Rinish is an online entrepreneur who founded Neophyte, LLC, a company whose mission is bringing high-end website services to the masses of lower capitalized startups, non-profits and local governments.

The primary brand under which Neophyte, LLC operates is Rinish.com. Rinish.com is a virtual based company that brings together experts in the various levels of the website industry such as design, development and marketing. The business model of Rinish.com focuses on bringing together experts in the online industry, acting as the project manager of the providing of services, therefore, allowing for the passing of affordable costs to the client.

In under two years of operating, Neophyte, LLC has become cash flow positive with a growth rate of nearly 50%. As a result, Mr. Rinish is asked to speak regarding his experience in founding and growing a Start Up online business with little start up capital using social networking and new media tools and techniques.
